    public class EntryServiceImpl
extends EntryServiceBaseImpl
    The implementation of the entry remote service.

    All custom service methods should be put in this class. Whenever methods are added, rerun ServiceBuilder to copy their definitions into the EntryService interface.

    This is a remote service. Methods of this service are expected to have security checks based on the propagated JAAS credentials because this service can be accessed remotely.

    benyedai
